casebody.data:
(September 7, 1962)

In decisions Nos. 1-6: Concur — Botein, P. J., Rabin, Stevens, Eager and Steuer, JJ.

Katie Pieeri et al. v. City of New York et al.

Motion granted insofar as to extend defendant-appellant’s time to procure the record on appeal and appellant’s points to be served and filed on or before September 11, 1962 with notice of argument for the October 1962 Term of this court, said appeal to be argued or submitted when reached.
